title: C.S.D. Galcasa
text: C.S.D. Galcasa was a Guatemalan <a href="association%20football">football</a> club, which won the <a href="Copa%20de%20Guatemala">Copa de Guatemala</a> in 1980, and were <a href="Liga%20Nacional%20de%20F%C3%BAtbol%20de%20Guatemala">Liga Nacional de Fútbol de Guatemala</a> runners-up in 1986.
